value.0: This is the ORSv5 Appearance Mirror. You can make your Character and Gear look how you wish here. Shields and Weapons are Modified at the Crafting Anvil (Crafting Skill Radial Menu).
You have to have Armor/Clothing equipped to make changes to ANY of your gear.
Select the item to Change Appearance.
You are changing your Head. If you wish to change your Helm please put on your Helm.
You are changing your Helm. If you wish to change your head please take off this Helm.
Select the item to Change Coloring.

<StartHighlight>[ Make Your Choices....Changes ARE Permanent ]</Start>


Note: Some Head Models Do Not Have Colorized Eyes and Lips
You can not modify your gear at this time. You may not have any adverse effects or be in shapechange while using this Mirror.
